  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to see transaction details in chat so that I can get more information.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Improvement\r\n\r\nWhen user A sends money in chat to user B the visualization lacks information, isn't actionable, and looks rather underwhelming.  \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nA user can see important transaction detail info in chat, and tap through for more info\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nOnly amount is shown\r\n\r\n<img width=\"317\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-04-26 at 4 41 10 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/116099/39312791-a8fbce0c-4970-11e8-9483-ab1c5c8ef0c4.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\nSend a transaction in chat\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\nWe can improve this by:\r\n\r\n- Showing more transaction info\r\n- Making it actionable with a link to transaction details screen\r\n- Give it a visual makeover",
